40|$|The goal of {{my thesis}} "Beginnings {{and history of}} <b>state</b> <b>interventions</b> into housing market using Czech market as example" is to {{illustrate}} circumstances (conditions) in which housing policy started to evolve. Next goal is to explain the reasons why <b>state</b> <b>interventions</b> on Czech housing market grew stronger. Historical circumstances, which were important in housing market shaping, are accompanied by analysis of historical sources. First part of thesis is focused on explaining basic terms regarding forming housing market and highlighting specialties of housing as (tady ten statek nevím). Second part demonstrates first <b>state</b> <b>interventions</b> in Czech Republic territory using historical legislative sources, statistical data and historical context. It starts in Austria-Hungary and then chronologically moves over two World Wars era and socialism to the present...|$|R
